        public static java.lang.String allInOne(java.lang.String appId)
        This method constructs a request string of a single application from omni model to instinct model.

      • allInOne

        public static java.lang.String allInOne(java.lang.String appId,
                                        java.lang.String instinctCall)
        This method constructs a request string of a single application from omni model to instinct model with additional parameter instinctCall indicating the judging phase from omni process.
        Parameters:
        appId - the application id of omni model to construct to instinct model.
        instinctCall - supports "preCheck", "finalCheck" and "update".
        Returns:
        resulting instinct string delimited by delimiter.
        Since:
        1.0.0
        See Also:
        allInOne(List)

      • allInOne

        public static java.util.List<java.lang.String> allInOne(java.util.List<java.lang.String> appIds)
        This method constructs a list of request strings from omni model to instinct model.
        Parameters:
        appIds - the list of application ids from omni model to construct to instinct model.
        Returns:
        a list of resulting instinct strings separated by line break and internally delimited by delimiter.
        See Also:
        allInOne(List)

      • allInOne

        public static java.util.List<java.lang.String> allInOne(java.util.List<java.lang.String> appIds,
                                                        java.lang.String instinctCall)
        This method constructs a list of request strings from omni model to instinct model with additional parameter instinctCall indicating the judging phase from omni process.
        Parameters:
        appIds - the list of application ids from omni model to construct to instinct model.
        instinctCall - supports "preCheck", "finalCheck" and "update".
        Returns:
        a list of resulting instinct strings separated by line break and internally delimited by delimiter.
        Since:
        1.0.0

      • singleBlackList

        public static java.lang.String singleBlackList(Application appblk,

        This method constructs a single black list string from omni model to instinct model.
